{"tid":1975403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"靜靜雞呀！ 點解我會係個藍絲口中聽到佢識前線手足","createTime":"2020-04-16T13:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T00:29:46.000Z","uid":63222,"like":93,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0507b64cdee93abe3acfa550d9e4d150cde20fb2","tid":1975403,"uid":63222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"講咗幾多次要靜靜雞<br />\n<br />\n今日食飯嘅時候聽到個藍絲話佢同事係前線<br />\n<br />\n之後我好奇問多兩句佢點知<br />\n<br />\n原來佢話手足同另一個同事講 再轉折聽番來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁姐係中間傳左幾多手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同事有幾熟都好  係黃都好  都唔好同人講做過d咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你永遠唔知佢有幾口疏   你唔知佢係咪扮黃<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n最重要係你唔會知有冇機會傳落d狗既耳度  比人順藤摸瓜</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n唔好亂講野呀   冇人知你有冇打Online game<br />\n<br />\n十個月啦講到口臭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"fd456e41b78c3ff87a40e7f5b96501d4307c70a4","tid":1975403,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:37:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81435588ec13467732064804b356e2f0e8006e60","tid":1975403,"uid":63222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"f30d08700b14181f68eaa41707bbf4f35c0b379c","tid":1975403,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"[抵抗三中商]推薦四本好書，看完成為香港民族少年少女吧！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1975405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1975405</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"192b3efb95ffff826f4df712fb256ce656b5868b","tid"